AWS CodeBuild
---------------
AWS CodeBuild is a fully managed build service that replaces Jenkins. It spins up a fresh container for each build, runs your buildspec.yml commands, and destroys the container after. No server to manage, no plugins to install, auto scales for parallel builds, and you only pay per build minute. In our pipeline CodePipeline is the orchestrator that triggers CodeBuild which does all the actual work — building JAR, running tests, building Docker image, pushing to ECR and deploying to EKS














